{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Bombs were raining all around us, but nobody was-- miraculously, nobody was killed from our camp people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were all in-- in-- in-- in safety and shelters or in the trenches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was just, you know-- an-- an incredible day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it gave us the greatest satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had waited for that day, prayed for that day to come to see this destroyed, because that would mean another setback for the German military.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this is exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know-- I could not-- I-- I never forget this day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- there where a lot of close calls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we finally crawled out of that crater-- but there was, like I said, an old bomb crater.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was from the previous war, just an isolated bomb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole airfield, everything was one giant cloud of dust, and we thought everything is destroyed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we just looked at us, and I think we were all--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we all thought this is the day we have waited for.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They finally did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- there are some others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, actually, during one of the air raids when the airport was not attacked, they-- they shot down a-- yeah, they shot down one of the accompanying Mustang fighters that accompanied the bomber periods.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- we actually saw the pilot, and turned out he was black.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans could not believe that they captured-- he surrendered to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
